flowchart TD
    A([Start: User Clicks Capture]) --> B[Frontend: Capture JPEG Blob]
    B --> C[Backend: Receive Image File]
    
    subgraph PreProcessing [Image Enhancement Layer]
        C --> D[Convert to Grayscale]
        D --> E[Apply 1.5x Contrast Boost]
    end

    E --> F{Extract Data}
    F --> G[Run Tesseract OCR]
    F --> H[Scan for Barcode]

    H -- Barcode Found --> I[Query Open Food Facts API]
    H -- No Barcode --> J[Analyze OCR Text via LLM]

    I --> K[Identify Category]
    J --> K

    K --> L{Assign Persona}
    L -- Food --> M[Persona: Food Scientist]
    L -- Textile --> N[Persona: Textile Expert]
    L -- Electronic --> O[Persona: Material Engineer]

    M & N & O --> P[Generate AI Analysis]
    P --> Q[Find 2 Best Alternatives]
    
    Q --> R[Return Data to Card Gallery]
    R --> S([End: UI Renders Product Card])
